<div class="tri-title"><h3>THIRD TRIMESTER QUESTION</h3></div>
  <div class="tri">
 <% if current_user.mother == true %>

    <%= form_for @user do |f|%>
        <%
         question_answered = false
         if current_user.tri_3_1 != nil &&
               current_user.tri_3_2 != nil &&
               current_user.tri_3_3 != nil
             question_answered = true
         end
        %>

      <p>1. Are you having headaches that are not relieved with over-the-counter
       medications or have visual changes associated with them, persistent vomiting,
       and upper abdominal pain?
         <p><% if question_answered == true %>
          <p><b><%= current_user.tri_3_1 %></b></p>
         <% end %></p>
      </p>

      <% if question_answered == false %>
        <ul>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_1, "Yes" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_1, "Yes" %>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_1, "No" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_1, "No" %>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_1, "N/A" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_1, "N/A" %>
        </ul>
      <% end %>


      <p>2. Is there decreased movement from your baby?
         <% if question_answered == true %>
           <p><b><%= current_user.tri_3_2 %></b></p>
         <% end %>
      </p>

      <% if question_answered == false %>
        <ul>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_2, "Yes" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_2, "Yes" %>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_2, "No" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_2, "No" %>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_2, "N/A" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_2, "N/A" %>
        </ul>
      <% end %>


      <p>3. Do any of these changes apply to you?  Vaginal discharge to a pink or
       reddish color, menstrual-like cramps, pressure in your pelvis or lower abdomen,
       and contractions that last for at least an hour that aren’t Braxton Hicks contractions.
         <% if question_answered == true %>
           <p><b><%= current_user.tri_3_3 %></b><p>
         <% end %>
      </p>

      <% if question_answered == false %>
        <ul>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_3, "Yes" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_3, "Yes" %>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_3, "No" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_3, "No" %>
           <%= f.label :tri_3_3, "N/A" %>
           <%= f.radio_button :tri_3_3, "N/A" %>
        </ul>
      <% end %>
    </div>

      <p><%= f.submit 'Reply' %></p>

    <% end %>

 <% else%>


     <p>
       1. Are you having headaches that are not relieved with over-the-counter
      medications or have visual changes associated with them, persistent vomiting,
      and upper abdominal pain?
        <ul><li><%= @user.tri_3_1 %></li></ul>
     </p>
     <p>
       2. Is there decreased movement from your baby?
        <ul><li><%= @user.tri_3_2 %></li></ul>
     </p>

     <p>
       3. Do any of these changes apply to you?  Vaginal discharge to a pink or
       reddish color, menstrual-like cramps, pressure in your pelvis or lower abdomen,
       and contractions that last for at least an hour that aren’t Braxton Hicks contractions.
       <ul><li><%= @user.tri_3_3 %></li></ul>
     </p>




 <% end %>

